{"TopicId":184279,"ForumId":148,"TopicTitle":"Kerbal Space Program Breaks Ground with a New DLC!","CreatedByName":"UomoCapra","CreatedById":167737,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-06T14:02:49Z","PageNum":19,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"thomash","CreatedById":160311,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T00:53:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is very good news.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Triop","CreatedById":145841,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T00:53:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Times New Roman\u0027, Times, serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:28px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#c0392b;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERobotics ? \u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Times New Roman\u0027, Times, serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:28px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#c0392b;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EALL ABOARD ! Free rides !\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/eTpxicplS5w?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T01:43:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:confused:\u0022\u003E\u00A0So What? How would experiments work I still don\u0027t get how?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T01:52:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595343\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557279785\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022196529\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Doodling Astronaut\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 minutes ago, The Doodling Astronaut said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:confused:\u0022\u003E\u00A0So What? How would experiments work I still don\u0027t get how?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou start it, make sure it has enough power, then wait. Once it is done the data can either be picked up manually or submitted via comnet if the base station has an antenna in range.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T01:55:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAh that makes more sense thanks \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/184845-mechbfp/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022184845\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/184845-mechbfp/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@MechBFP\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ger_space","CreatedById":167349,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T02:56:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595103\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557254005\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002271012\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022theonegalen\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, theonegalen said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/106975-angel-125/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022106975\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/106975-angel-125/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Angel-125\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EAlthough if KK-lite became part of stock or DLC, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167349-ger_space/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022167349\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167349-ger_space/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Ger_space\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0would probably commit modder sudoku. And that would make me sad.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot really, I would be happy so throw away all no longer needed code and I would have more time to play the game than spending all nights modding.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Aegolius13","CreatedById":165625,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T03:16:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHoping the ground experiments will\u00A0 be something more than \u0022click, wait, get science points,\u0022 like the MPL tends to be.\u00A0 But also hoping\u00A0they\u0027re not too grindy, like the \u0022take readings at 5 points\u0022 contracts.\u00A0 I guess I don\u0027t have a good idea about make ground science entertaining within the constraints of the base game mechanics, but hoping they\u0027ve figured it out.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe robotic parts alone look like they\u0027re probably worth the cost, though, so anything else is gravy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"lodiped","CreatedById":104431,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T04:11:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223594994\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557244814\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022125662\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Snark\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, Snark said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo your theory is that they should spend a whole bunch of money to make a thing, and then give it away for free?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nExcept I pretty clearly did not say that, did I? If you read it, carefully this time, you will realise that I support selling stuff... that doesn\u0027t belong in the core of the experience. Like I said, if a company wants to sells aesthetical things after the full release, then do it, there will always be content for it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBy your standards,\u00A0bugfixes and patches should be behind a paywall too, shouldn\u0027t it? They\u0027re working on a product and they need to sell the product... So, do you want a functioning game after you bought it??? Well, buy the bugfixes too, of course. That\u0027s how the industry works! \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223594994\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557244814\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022125662\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Snark\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, Snark said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s how commerce \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Eworks\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mean, I get it, man.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223594994\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557244814\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022125662\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Snark\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, Snark said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey\u0027re not going to build a thing unless they think they can make money at it,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, I get it, I really do.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223594994\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557244814\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022125662\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Snark\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, Snark said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen you walk into a grocery store, you gotta pay money if you want to walk out with stuff to eat.\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, yeah. So you go in to buy a candy, you get out of the store and when you open the candy you see there\u0027s only half in there, \u0022oh well\u0022, you think, \u0022it\u0027s one of them candies, isn\u0027t it?\u0022,\u00A0so you go back into the store and give the guy another buck so you can finally have the full candy you originally paid for. That\u0027s very reasonable, of course.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223594994\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557244814\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022125662\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Snark\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, Snark said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nand practically every KSP player will buy it\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF[...]\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffff00;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003EAnd the players\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#353c41;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffff00;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003Ewin\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#353c41;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffff00;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E.\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#353c41;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#353c41;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n:sigh:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MajorFizz31","CreatedById":196242,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T04:12:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan the staff please give any information on what\u0027s happening with console? Do you have a team working on catching console up to PC or are you putting all your time into PC? I mean, you have now put out two updates since console went to 1.0.1.3 after a year on xbox. What\u0027s going on in that department??\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-05-08T04:18:49Z\u0022 title=\u002205/08/2019 04:18  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMay 8, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by MajorFizz31\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EIncorrect information\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ElJugador","CreatedById":18783,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T04:14:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595381\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557285410\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022165625\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Aegolius13\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n54 minutes ago, Aegolius13 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHoping the ground experiments will\u00A0 be something more than \u0022click, wait, get science points,\u0022 like the MPL tends to be.\u00A0 But also hoping\u00A0they\u0027re not too grindy, like the \u0022take readings at 5 points\u0022 contracts.\u00A0 I guess I don\u0027t have a good idea about make ground science entertaining within the constraints of the base game mechanics, but hoping they\u0027ve figured it out.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe robotic parts alone look like they\u0027re probably worth the cost, though, so anything else is gravy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe surface survey contracts are probably the flat-out best in the entire game, because they\u0027re not too wildly spaced apart to be boring to drive between but far enough to be a nontrivial distance from each other. Giving you a real reason to use rovers, which are probably my favorite method of getting around on the surface of a world.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T04:49:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595396\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557288699\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104431\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022lodiped\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n36 minutes ago, lodiped said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E you read it, carefully this time, you will realise that I support selling stuff... that doesn\u0027t belong in the core of the experie\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003En\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003Ece.\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo basically you only support them selling stuff that no one actually wants then? Because that is exactly what would happen.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T05:55:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595396\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557288699\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104431\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022lodiped\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, lodiped said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBy\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E your standards,\u00A0bugfixes and patches should be behind a paywall too, shouldn\u0027t it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are three tiers of post-release content: things that everybody thinks should be free, things that everybody thinks is ok to be paid, and the contentious stuff that some are ok paying for and others think should be free.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027ll be hard pressed to find someone outside the boardrooms out the worst companies who thinks bug fixes should be paid.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSkins and dances and that garbage can be paid. I don\u0027t want it anyway and wouldn\u0027t probably download it even if it was free.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut if they want to keep the lights on, they need to charge for something that\u0027s actually worth paying for.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VoidCosmos","CreatedById":192336,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T07:42:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595200\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557264641\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289439\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022StrandedonEarth\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, StrandedonEarth said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey\u2019ll probably drop a light 1.8 as a base for BG\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey will surely do this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Yakuzi","CreatedById":85181,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T07:43:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223594668\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557188618\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002235181\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022katateochi\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/7/2019 at 2:23 AM, katateochi said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWill the stock system have something akin to IR\u0027s sequencer? Cos that\u0027s a really essential part of anything more than a basic arm.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595142\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557258278\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022113764\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Foxster\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, Foxster said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do we think \u0022spider leg motion\u0022 is going to work?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m guessing we are going to get motorised joints, hinges and\u00A0electric motors, etc. So how will we make the timing work so that we can operate the parts in a sequence to make multi-leg craft walk?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027s a new controller system, which allows you to coordinate robotic movement. From the PC Gamer \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.pcgamer.com/uk/kerbal-space-programs-next-dlc-adds-robotics-and-more-experiments-embargoed/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Earticle\u003C/a\u003E on Breaking Ground:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003E\u0022Your rover\u0027s arms aren\u0027t the only fancy bit of robotic kit that you\u0027ll be able to take advantage of. Robotic hinges, pistons, rotors and rotational servos can be stuck onto spaceships, each of them with simulated physics affected things like force, torque and power consumption. These components and other parts of your ship can also be controlled via the new robotic controller system, which lets you coordinate their behaviour.\u0022\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/160254-maxsimal/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022160254\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/160254-maxsimal/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Maxsimal\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/em\u003E \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167737-uomocapra/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022167737\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167737-uomocapra/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@UomoCapra\u003C/a\u003E, I take it the new planetary surface features have colliders, does the current terrain scatter also get colliders? And are planet textures and geography updated, or will it still be the same bland terrain we have now?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUnlike Making History, I\u0027m seriously considering buying this DLC depending on how the new features are implemented and what the reviews say. I may even consider venturing beyond Minmus now that there\u0027s actually something worth exploring (hopefully). Looking forward to hear the details!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T07:57:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLTTP as usual but I love this. I\u0027ve been a bit burned out on KSP but this looks like just the thing to rekindle the old flame.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you manage to fix the surface interaction issues so bases stay where they\u0027re put and don\u0027t completely kill the framerate, I will be your happiest customer ever.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"050644zf","CreatedById":173201,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T09:34:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAccording to first pic, are\u00A0there light belts on the edge of new space suit?\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Chel","CreatedById":176173,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T10:48:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWill this be coming out for console in like 6 months or something too? I\u0027m curious\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T11:37:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595499\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557312537\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022176173\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The_Cat_In_Space\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n48 minutes ago, The_Cat_In_Space said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWill this be coming out for console in like 6 months or something too? I\u0027m curious\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe won\u0027t know until SQUAD announces it, which probably won\u0027t be for several months at least.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T12:16:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595499\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557312537\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022176173\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The_Cat_In_Space\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, The_Cat_In_Space said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWill this be coming out for console in like 6 months or something too? I\u0027m curious\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPretty much guaranteed to come to console, as that is likely a rather large chunk of their user base pie.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHopefully it doesn\u2019t take as long this time, but I guess that depends on how difficult the robotics interfaces is to use and if it could be ported over without major changes.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kardea","CreatedById":68737,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T14:07:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo... basically stock Infernal Robotics and stock Surface Experiment Pack? Heck yeah! Solid content, Squad. Bringing popular/loved mods into the \u0027official\u0027 fold (and adding new content to them...) is 100% what I want to see in future DLC.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n(stock AVP/\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Environmental Visual Enhancement (mod)\u0022\u003EEVE\u003C/abbr\u003E/Scatterer and stock Outer Planets Mod/Kopernicus in the future, maybe..? And maybe just pay \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/105588-cobaltwolf/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022105588\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/105588-cobaltwolf/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@CobaltWolf\u003C/a\u003E some $$$ and straight-up add his BDB parts? They\u0027re practically essential at this point.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T14:08:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI will ask what is the best thing?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like the fact that there is a point for bases and that rovers will be better than ever\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DriftedCougar","CreatedById":197372,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T14:09:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223594125\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557151369\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022167737\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022UomoCapra\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/6/2019 at 4:02 PM, UomoCapra said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBrand new robotic\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLooks really cool!, also...i do not like rating grammar but this just annoys me:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nShouldnt it be brand new robotics?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Angelo Kerman","CreatedById":106975,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T14:11:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595372\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557284202\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022167349\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ger_space\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, Ger_space said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot really, I would be happy so throw away all no longer needed code and I would have more time to play the game than spending all nights modding.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLikewise. If the stock SEP could work in orbit, I could retire WBI Science. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Eskandare","CreatedById":62742,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T14:56:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595573\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557324663\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022106975\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Angel-125\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n41 minutes ago, Angel-125 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLikewise. If the stock SEP could work in orbit, I could retire WBI Science. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeh I like SEP as it is one of the core mods I use in my non-dev install. And of course WBI (which I need for the new rotors mechanics and the helicarrier in CVX.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VoidCosmos","CreatedById":192336,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-08T15:09:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595605\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557327366\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002262742\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Eskandare\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 minutes ago, Eskandare said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeh I like SEP as it is one of the core mods I use in my non-dev install. And of course WBI (which I need for the new rotors mechanics and the helicarrier in CVX.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just started to us CVX a day ago\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}